“The sea is ours”: Bolivia, blocked, hopes that the court will reopen the path to the Pacific
Sailors patrol in an armored boat in the Naval Headquarters La Paz.
Public buildings carry a flag as blue as the ocean.
From Lake Titicaca to the Amazon, the naval bases display the following motorcycle: "The sea is rightfully ours.
