Toyota’s production line is operated in “tight flow”, parts arrive every 37 minutes from UK and EU suppliers for custom-made vehicles.
If the UK leaves the EU on 29 March without a deal, there could be disruptions at the border that, according to the industry, could lead to delays and shortages of coins.
